{"tid":1553424,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"鬼可以唔捉，但唔可以唔防","createTime":"2019-09-08T15:12:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T16:39:13.000Z","uid":80972,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"92609674a5eb83de94281b5d3fe00621ab8db367","tid":1553424,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:12:02.000Z","msg":"D狗扮人都有<br />\n1) 螢光/鮮色狗帶或狗貼<br />\n2) 仲同行最少3,4個人<br />\n3) 有機會出現槍袋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">正常勇武都唔會有呢d記應，但班狗一定要有明顯記應，唔係d武警替工唔識記人</span><br />\n<br />\n有鬼嘅問題係<br />\n1. 令前線被捕風險極高，一來鬼會報告大隊行蹤，二來鬼會自己拉人<br />\n2. 會帶風向，會搞事，影響前線部署<br />\n<br />\n捉鬼一黎會影響前線，二黎都好危險，因為佢地有真槍，佢地狗命有危險係會開槍<br />\n<br />\n但我覺得可以防範<br />\n每次行動都開個狗帶報料區<br />\n將<span style=\"color: red;\">當日狗帶款色公開討論</span><br />\n務求令呢班餓狗嘅行動成本提高<br />\n<br />\n討論下，不喜勿屌"},{"pid":"b86ed21c354c81a8f8318fd7fae135a2ba0708bb","tid":1553424,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:12:37.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"ca5229f2278d49947d8ba4b935d8976e0284f696","tid":1553424,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:14:02.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"be3b4dca6335c1a97679dc8186cd684fe8321592","tid":1553424,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:14:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7f7d5cdc50c9388cbeb59efefc719a7997293974","tid":1553424,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />push  push"},{"pid":"8d284469bd538e1cf218e90af9431ada2dafb131","tid":1553424,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:15:32.000Z","msg":"sorry 借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻煩未食飯既同我入哂黎!!! 唔準有人餓住個肚!!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《急推》 前線唔好餓死呀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1540938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1540938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5fac7ef3c8846972aab2a6e9623137e78763658b","tid":1553424,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:16:00.000Z","msg":"push push<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc113f2ef62574365a9c82a4b7ce4d9eeb21a34b","tid":1553424,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:16:20.000Z","msg":"唔捉又點防"},{"pid":"8663ab69a1da0978791be2e60f6289cad7d5867b","tid":1553424,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:16:33.000Z","msg":"push push push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ddb9335749b04808c44663f68dcbe0307e0ac2","tid":1553424,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:18:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/passiontimes/videos/1643060702491544/?epa=SEARCH_BOX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpassiontimes%2Fvideos%2F1643060702491544%2F%3Fepa%3DSEARCH_BOX&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BqhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=02205112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/passiontimes/videos/1643060702491544/?epa=SEARCH_BOX</a><br />\n<br />\n但個女鬼幾靚,捉到既話應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3095dcc864dff590dd2315e374df3ef3f22da51e","tid":1553424,"uid":114725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:23:00.000Z","msg":"如果卧底枝槍唔見咗，啲狗又敢唔敢認自己係警察，卧底？"},{"pid":"3037f2814499a43c0932e842f31cd13cc8087597","tid":1553424,"uid":39427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:24:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">識唱嘅大家一齊唱</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BqhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=11aa919b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>《願榮光歸香港》  </strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Glory be to thee, Hong Kong</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">In angst, tears are shed o&rsquo;er this Land</span><br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">With rage, fears are crushed, in arms we stand</span><br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">We rise, undefiled, our voice shall never die</span><br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡  <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">As we yearn, our freedom nighs</span><br />\n<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">With eyes blinded, long it comes the night</span><br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">In faith, banners high, we pledge to fight</span><br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Our flesh, sacrificed, our blood shall write this song</span><br />\n建自由 光輝 香港  <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Free this Land, &ldquo;Stand with Hong Kong!&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Stars will fall, and darkness fills the air</span><br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Storms will break, bedazzled by our gallant flares!</span><br />\n捍自由   <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">We shall strike</span><br />\n來齊集這裡  <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">This perilous night</span><br />\n來全力抗對  <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Determined to fight</span><br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">With hope, with song, with dignity!</span><br />\n<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Glory enshrined, break our chains! Hold our lines!</span><br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Freedom shall rise! Revolution of our Time!</span><br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Liberty thrives, rights divine, in our unending strides</span><br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Glory be to thee, Hong Kong!</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q4kAzyW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ4kAzyW.jpg&h=84f48da3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">英文譯版原post<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》英文歌詞 &quot;Glory be to Thee, Hong Kong&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547782\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547782</a></span>"},{"pid":"4dfdf5b8ef550bc00ae0921c266c7d0fbd136cfc","tid":1553424,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:26:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FZNrKRd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFZNrKRd.gif&h=a7816cba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/i4Ji8E6Hq34\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fi4Ji8E6Hq34&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BqhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=1307738e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/i4Ji8E6Hq34</a><br />\n疑似大陸武警/解放軍<br />\n20秒 用普通話講 左邊左邊<br />\n<br />\n現場只有記者 冇人衝擊 亦冇舉旗叫人散去"},{"pid":"c661c9997bc5c9173b33073d6a6cbfb29833a874","tid":1553424,"uid":305009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc113f2ef62574365a9c82a4b7ce4d9eeb21a34b","tid":1553424,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:16:20.000Z","msg":"唔捉又點防"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:27:58.000Z","msg":"Boycott ghost<br />\n例如提身邊人,之後點做就睇現場"},{"pid":"6ac649a90c0995127275c9645ec356332f92f086","tid":1553424,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc113f2ef62574365a9c82a4b7ce4d9eeb21a34b","tid":1553424,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy